<div id="pf363e" class="pf w63 h237" data-page-no="363e"><div class="pc pc363e w63 h237"><div class="t m1a34 x53 h4d y6c6 ff3 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Blessing of Daily Study </div><div class="t m1578 x34 h27 yef1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Every day some portion of time should be appropriated </div><div class="t m558 x74 h27 y17c8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the study of the lessons, not merely in learning to me-</div><div class="t m5f5 x74 h27 yce7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chanically repeat the words, while the mind does not com-</div><div class="t mb5 x74 h27 y2d7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prehend the meaning; but to go to the very foundation, and </div><div class="t mf5 x73 h27 ye05 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">become familiar with what is brought out in the lesson.&quot; </div><div class="t m1f0 x74 h16 y1289 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">â€”Counsels on Sabbath School </div><div class="t m8df x8f h27 y794 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Work, page 53. </div><div class="t m1195 x9c h4d ya32 ff3 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My Pledge </div><div class="t m93f x34 h27 y1447 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As one who greatly desires to improve his knowledge of </div><div class="t m689 x74 h27 y1305 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Scriptures, I pledge myself to the careful and prayerful </div><div class="t m1f1 x73 h27 y7fd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of some portion of my Sabbath School lesson each </div><div class="t mcfb x74 h27 yc3f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day of the week. </div><div class="t m2dd x99 h34 y96b ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(signed) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
